Package: bccp
Title: Bin-Conditional Conformal Prediction
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sentinel Team", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "sentinel@example.com")
Description: Implements bin-conditional conformal prediction (BCCP) for
    generating valid prediction intervals with coverage guarantees within
    user-specified outcome bins. Includes extensions for handling seasonality
    and non-stationarity in time series data. Based on Blair, Coppock & Moor
    (2024) <arXiv:2410.14507>.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Imports:
    dplyr,
    stats
Suggests:
    ggplot2,
    tidyr,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://lassa-sentinel.github.io/bccp/, https://github.com/lassa-sentinel/bccp
